Manni,

292
00:14:10,763 --> 00:14:11,444
she's awake.

293
00:14:11,684 --> 00:14:12,564
Come up.

294
00:14:21,204 --> 00:14:23,483
The truth will come out eventually.

295
00:14:23,843 --> 00:14:25,284
And I've always insisted

296
00:14:25,284 --> 00:14:26,924
that you must leave this place.

297
00:14:27,123 --> 00:14:28,164
It's for your own good.

298
00:14:28,483 --> 00:14:30,243
Do you remember
what happened last night?

299
00:14:30,843 --> 00:14:31,843
Let me remind you.

300
00:14:32,084 --> 00:14:33,204
I can't promise

301
00:14:33,843 --> 00:14:35,044
I'll arrive in time next time.

302
00:14:36,243 --> 00:14:38,123
You're dodging the main issue.

303
00:14:38,523 --> 00:14:40,363
You're afraid of me staying here

304
00:14:40,564 --> 00:14:41,964
and uncovering the truth,

305
00:14:42,084 --> 00:14:42,964
right?

306
00:14:43,164 --> 00:14:43,964
Afraid?

307
00:14:49,684 --> 00:14:50,603
Afraid of what?

308
00:14:52,603 --> 00:14:54,044
A clear conscience fears

309
00:14:54,763 --> 00:14:56,084
no ghosts.

310
00:14:56,603 --> 00:14:58,164
But you know best.

311
00:15:04,964 --> 00:15:05,684
Morning, Mr. Tu.

312
00:15:06,204 --> 00:15:07,164
Take her away.

313
00:15:12,003 --> 00:15:12,843
Let's go.

314
00:15:17,204 --> 00:15:18,404
For tonight's Beauty Contest,

315
00:15:18,603 --> 00:15:19,723
have her participate too.

316
00:15:23,044 --> 00:15:23,843
Okay.

317
00:15:28,763 --> 00:15:29,843
Drugging the wine,

318
00:15:31,003 --> 00:15:32,723
and asking Lin Shen to pick her up

319
00:15:33,483 --> 00:15:34,363
were your doing, huh?

320
00:15:34,444 --> 00:15:35,964
No, Mr. Tu, it wasn't me.

321
00:15:36,204 --> 00:15:36,924
It wasn't me.

322
00:15:36,924 --> 00:15:39,044
When did you become so vile?

323
00:15:42,404 --> 00:15:43,040
Mr. Tu,

324
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:43,603
trust me.

325
00:15:43,603 --> 00:15:44,723
I really didn't do it.

326
00:15:44,763 --> 00:15:46,284
I was just following your orders

327
00:15:46,284 --> 00:15:47,564
to teach Su Yunian a lesson.

328
00:15:47,564 --> 00:15:48,483
As for Lin Shen,

329
00:15:48,483 --> 00:15:50,044
I told him to take her home.

330
00:15:50,044 --> 00:15:51,763
I truly had no idea this video existed.

331
00:15:51,843 --> 00:15:52,404
I...

332
00:15:52,684 --> 00:15:53,843
You have to believe me.

333
00:15:53,843 --> 00:15:55,883
I don't know who wants to harm her.

334
00:15:55,924 --> 00:15:56,804
But no matter what,

335
00:15:56,804 --> 00:15:57,843
it couldn't be me.

336
00:15:57,843 --> 00:15:59,763
I have no reason to harm her.

337
00:16:00,084 --> 00:16:01,723
Mr. Tu, please believe me.

338
00:16:01,723 --> 00:16:03,603
If I may say something,

339
00:16:03,603 --> 00:16:05,643
Mr. Tu, please don't get so worked up.

340
00:16:05,804 --> 00:16:08,363
There might be a misunderstanding.

341
00:16:08,363 --> 00:16:11,044
Miss Bai is usually kind-hearted.

342
00:16:11,044 --> 00:16:13,483
Seems she wouldn't do
such a malicious thing.

343
00:16:13,883 --> 00:16:15,404
This requires careful consideration.

344
00:16:15,404 --> 00:16:17,164
We must investigate thoroughly.

345
00:16:20,843 --> 00:16:22,723
Thank Mr. Tang for pleading for you.

346
00:16:23,603 --> 00:16:24,123
Yes.

347
00:16:24,284 --> 00:16:25,044
Yes, Mr. Tu.

348
00:16:25,044 --> 00:16:25,843
However,

349
00:16:27,643 --> 00:16:28,804
you may be spared from death,

350
00:16:29,404 --> 00:16:30,523
yet still doomed to suffer.

351
00:16:30,924 --> 00:16:32,284
Once I uncover the truth,

352
00:16:32,444 --> 00:16:33,763
when everything comes to light,

353
00:16:34,444 --> 00:16:35,603
if it was you,

354
00:16:37,324 --> 00:16:38,123
the consequences...

355
00:16:45,964 --> 00:16:46,964
Thank you, Mr. Tu.

356
00:16:49,284 --> 00:16:50,444
Thank you, Mr. Tang.

357
00:16:57,404 --> 00:16:58,404
Thank you.

358
00:17:17,043 --> 00:17:19,164
Since that's settled,

359
00:17:19,164 --> 00:17:21,364
we look forward to Mr. Tu and Mr. Zhao

360
00:17:21,364 --> 00:17:23,043
attending punctually tomorrow, okay?

361
00:17:26,364 --> 00:17:27,164
Mr. Tu?

362
00:17:27,844 --> 00:17:28,644
Mr. Tu?

363
00:17:29,003 --> 00:17:29,444
Mr. Tu?

364
00:17:29,444 --> 00:17:30,124
You chat first.

365
00:17:30,124 --> 00:17:30,803
I have to go.

366
00:17:31,644 --> 00:17:33,124
Mr. Tu.

367
00:17:33,124 --> 00:17:34,644
Let me drink with you.

368
00:17:34,964 --> 00:17:36,483
Okay.

369
00:17:36,483 --> 00:17:37,523
Keep singing.

370
00:17:39,763 --> 00:17:40,563
Hello, Mr. Tu.

371
00:17:40,684 --> 00:17:41,844
Enjoy the drinks.

372
00:17:41,844 --> 00:17:42,844
Enjoy the singing.

373
00:17:43,444 --> 00:17:44,243
Su Yunian.

374
00:17:44,723 --> 00:17:46,523
Enjoy the fun too!

375
00:17:49,323 --> 00:17:50,124
Jiasheng,

376
00:17:51,444 --> 00:17:52,444
tonight,

377
00:17:53,124 --> 00:17:55,404
I'll give you

378
00:17:55,763 --> 00:18:02,003
a taste of old dreams rekindled.

379
00:18:11,444 --> 00:18:15,118
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

380
00:18:15,417 --> 00:18:18,608
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

381
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:24,061
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

382
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:27,409
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

383
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:32,610
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

384
00:18:32,834 --> 00:18:36,331
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

385
00:18:37,730 --> 00:18:41,417
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

386
00:18:42,055 --> 00:18:47,170
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

387
00:18:47,874 --> 00:18:52,008
♪I feel guilty♪

388
00:18:52,578 --> 00:18:56,322
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

389
00:18:57,186 --> 00:19:00,629
♪Even in tears♪

390
00:19:01,378 --> 00:19:05,292
♪It doesn't matter♪

391
00:19:05,474 --> 00:19:09,297
♪We embrace in dreams♪

392
00:19:10,146 --> 00:19:13,584
♪I let down all my defenses♪

393
00:19:14,818 --> 00:19:18,181
♪Though the story has its end♪

394
00:19:18,946 --> 00:19:27,298
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
